object.name: Audit Trail
object.simulatedExtractionQuery:
SELECT *
CONTACT CONTACT
  LEFT CONTACT_COM_METHOD CONTACT_COM_METHOD ON ccm.CONTACT_GID = c.CONTACT_GID
  LEFT NOTIFY_SUBJECT_CONTACT NOTIFY_SUBJECT_CONTACT ON nsc.CONTACT_GID = c.CONTACT_GID AND nsc.COM_METHOD_GID = ccm.COM_METHOD_GID
WHERE
  c.DOMAIN_NAME = 'BAU'
  AND
  c.CONTACT_GID = 'BAU.AUD'
ORDER BY
  c.CONTACT_GID,
  ccm.COM_METHOD_RANK,
  nsc.NOTIFY_SUBJECT_GID
